{
  "id": "adv_main_03_01_04",
  "title": "BIG4編1章4話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage01",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tokyodorm-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様。何を観てるんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good work. What are you watching?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "あ……{user}さん、お疲れ様です\nサニピがこの間出演した歌番組を観てたんですけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… {user}-san‚ good work\nI was watching the music show Sunny Peace appeared on recently…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "最近のサニピ、ほんとに凄いねって話してたんです\n私達でもびっくりするくらいキラキラしてるっていうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We were just talking about how amazing Sunny Peace has been lately\nThey're shining so brightly‚ it's even surprising to us",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.4433333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "BIG4入りしてから、歌もダンスも……\nさらに磨きがかかりましたね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since joining the BIG4‚ their singing and dancing…\nHave become even more polished",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……本当に凄いと思うよ\nみんなの調子はどうだ？　明日はライブバトルだろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true… I think they're really amazing\nHow are you all feeling? Tomorrow's the live battle‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "準備は十分出来ています。全力を尽くします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're fully prepared. We'll do our best",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "でも……ここのところ、自分達が勝つイメージが\nうまく湧かなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… lately‚ I can't seem to imagine\nUs winning…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、ちょっと考え過ぎじゃないかな～\n最近表情が硬いよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono‚ aren't you overthinking it a bit\nYour expression has been stiff lately‚ you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 54.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "はい、むに～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Here‚ moony",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃ、ひゃめて、ほっぺた掴まないで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hya‚ stop it‚ don't grab my cheeks…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "やめませーん。ほらほら、にこーって笑って？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I won't stop. Come on‚ smile like \"nico\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "に、にこぉ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ni‚ nico…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "あはは！　琴乃ちゃん、顔怖ーい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha! Kotono‚ your face is scary!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "怖い顔で笑うってどういうことですの！？\n琴乃、私にも顔を見せなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How can you smile with such a scary face!?\nKotono‚ show me your face too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、私達も最近、表情が硬くなってましたね\nみんなで笑顔の練習をしましょうか。はい、すずちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ we've all had stiff expressions lately‚ haven't we?\nShall we practice smiling together? Here‚ Suzu",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃわぁぁぁ！？　引っ張り過ぎですわ！\nもうちょっと優しく！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyawaaa!? You're pulling too hard!\nBe a little gentler!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめんなさい\nそれなら……こんな感じでどうでしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry\nThen… how about this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "はふぅ……この適度な力加減……\nにゃかにゃかやりましゅわねぇ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hafu… This moderate force…\nIt's nyaka-nyaka…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "凄い、すずにゃんてば寝ちゃった\nじゃあ次は芽衣の番ね！　よろしく、沙季ちゃん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Amazing‚ Suzu-nyan fell asleep\nThen it's Mei's turn next! Please‚ Saki",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "はいはい、それじゃあいきますよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ okay‚ shall we start?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "ふにゃぁ～……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Funya…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "あはは。じゃあ今日は、明日の本番に向けて\nみんなで笑顔の練習だね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha. So today‚ for tomorrow's main event\nWe're practicing smiling together",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "うん……そうね。しっかり練習しておこっか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… that's right. Let's practice properly",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_moon-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 134.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、じゃあ芽衣はすずにゃんのわき腹担当で！\nうりうりうり～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ then Mei will be in charge of Suzu-nyan's sides!\nTickle tickle tickle",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、芽衣！？　笑顔の練習なのになんで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ Mei!? We're practicing smiling‚ so why…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "あはははは！？　ちょ、ほんとにやめあはははは！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahahahaha!? Wait‚ really‚ stahahap!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 150.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "な、渚……？\nなんで手をわきわきさせてるの……！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Na‚ Nagisa…?\nWhy are you wiggling your hands…!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（元気がないから心配してたけど……）\n（いつもの月ストらしくなってきたな、良かった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I was worried because they seemed down…)\n(But they're back to being like the usual Moon Tempest‚ that's good)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、俺はそろそろ行くよ\nみんな、あまり遅くならないようにな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ I'll be going now\nDon't stay up too late‚ everyone",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04/sud_vo_adv_main_03_01_04-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "あ、良かったら、途中まで一緒に行きませんか？\n琴乃ちゃんと帰ろうと思って",
      "translations": {
